1. [discipline:default] [project/autonomy-policy]
   gm autonomy policy (committed 2026-04-25): once a PRD is written, agents EXECUTE through to COMPLETE without asking the user. Forbidden patterns: "should I continue", "want me to do X", offering to split work, pre-confirmation before multi-file edits. Asking permitted ONLY as last resort for destructive-irreversible decisions or genuinely ambiguous user intent. Prefer exec:pause (renames .gm/prd.y…

